                <note rend="inline" type="source">717.2114/85: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Nicaragua</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Eberhardt</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-02-08T12:00:00-05:45"
                            >February 8, 1929—noon</date>.<lb/>[Received 2:55 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>43. Department’s 23, February 2, 8 p.m. In compliance with the Department’s
                    instructions I have again discussed the matter with the <pb facs="1071" n="935"
                        xml:id="pg_935"/> President and he told me that he would urge approval of
                    the treaty during the present session of Congress.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Eberhardt</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
